  "texts": [
    "The survey was disseminated through multiple channels, including email to registered users, in-app prompts, and via social media to acquire a balanced and extensive set of responses.",
    "Key findings from the survey encapsulated diverse aspects of user interaction and satisfaction with the system:",
    "High Degree of Personalization: Users generally lauded the system's ability to formulate travel recommendations which resonated closely with their preferences and stipulations.",
    "Qeios, CC-BY 4.0 • Article, March 5, 2024 Qeios ID: UYRUWT • https://doi.org/10.32388/UYRUWT 31/50",
    "Interface Usability: A mix of feedback was received concerning platform's user interface; while some found it intuitive and user-friendly, a subset expressed a desire for a more simplified and guided user journey."
  ]
}